'''Eickarie''' was the language spoken by the [[Reptile/Legends|reptilian]] [[Eickarie]]. In their culture, "left-handed" was associated with evil and deceit while "right-handed" was associated with good and truth.

==Words and phrases==
*''Shak'' was the Eickarie word for ''ready''.
*''Ha-ran mish-ra hee-sae sha-kae drof-si-shae-ral'' translated to "I am [[Ha-ran]] of the Family [[Mish-ra]], Clan [[Sha-kae]], [[Prince/Legends|prince]] of the Tribe [[Si-shae-ral]]."
*''Sha-mees craa shes-ayi'' translated to "I have praised their valor in your name; I trust that is acceptable."

